# Vercel builds ONLY the Next.js web app at the repo root.
#
# apps/desktop is a standalone Electron client with its OWN package.json and
# package-lock.json. Uploading it makes Vercel's framework/root-directory
# detection ambiguous (two lockfiles, a non-Next project) which can lead to the
# wrong build output and a platform-level 404 (NOT_FOUND). The web app never
# imports from it, so exclude it entirely.
apps/
